name: Large Fry
description:
This is a promotional NFT by the Koi collection @ https://koi.faithgrace.co.uk
It is given to the NFT community for zero XTZ

Entitled Large Fry. Someone will always think they are bigger than you. Have some guts and turn around and punch them in the eye :-)

” Koi or more specifically Nishikigoi are coloured varieties of the Amur carp that are kept for decorative purposes in outdoor Koi ponds or water gardens. Modern Japanese Koi are believed to date back to early 19th-century Japan where wild, colourful carp were caught, kept and bred by rice farmers “


Please be fair and take one copy only. If you take one we ask you to spread the word.
